name: BabySleepWell
0:
”Alexa, open Baby Sleep Well”
”Alexa, start Baby Sleep Well”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby sleep well
des:
It plays a sound of womb, with which most of babies feel relaxed and sleepy. 

It is recommended for not only babies but also 'anyone' who is living stressful life and wishes to have a good sleep.

It keeps playing until you say "Alexa Stop". (For a device which don't support Audio Player interface, it stops in one minute due to the limitation of SSML.)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
